Welcome to 95 Burnett Apartments, an intimate community with a charming atmosphere.
Our apartment community is located in Downtown Renton, Washington – a vibrant neighborhood brimming with boutique shops, restaurants and parks, all within walking distance from your front door.
Choose from eight spacious floor plans with studio, one, two and three bedroom options including two level townhomes.

Each home is tailored with amenities such as hardwood floors, 9’ ceilings, private balconies/patios, fully equipped kitchens with granite countertops, in-home washer and dryer and select homes feature vaulted ceilings.
Plus, enjoy our year round firepit and BBQ gazebo and play ping pong, cornhole, or putt-putt golf with your friends, family or neighbors on our second floor patio deck!
Living at 95 Burnett Apartments in Renton gives you easy access to I-405, and we are just a few miles from Tukwila Station for a quick commute to Seattle and Tacoma on the Sounder train.
Flying out for business or pleasure?
We're just six miles from Seattle-Tacoma International Airport.
Our convenient location also puts you within minutes to Boeing, Renton Landing, Southcenter Mall, Gene Coulon Memorial Beach Park and Cedar River Park.
We’d love to have you call 95 Burnett your new home.
Give us a call to schedule your tour today!
